name: Marosca Inu
description: Marosca Inu ($MAROSCA) is the first World Cup themed dog token on the Ethereum network. To celebrate Cristiano Ronaldo's final world cup of his illustrious career, we present his Labrador: Marosca! Marosca Inu is not simply a meme token, but also a utility token. Marosca will introduce a World Cup themed crypto fantasy game. Investors can use their $MAROSCA tokens to participate in the game, and if they do well, they mulitiply their tokens.
